<div class="fn p" id="FN2"><p id="P69"><strong>Conflicts of Interest</strong>: HK is the recipient of a research grant from Medtronic, Inc. through Yale University and is chair of a cardiac scientific advisory board for UnitedHealth.</p></div>
<div class="fn p" id="FN3"><p id="P70"><strong>Author Contributions</strong>: AL and LC conceived the study. AL, ES, EC, HK, EB, and LC acquired the data. AL, ES, EC, and LC performed the data analysis and interpretation. AL and LC drafted the manuscript and all authors contributed substantially to its revision. AL had full access to all of the data in the study and takes responsibility for the paper as a whole.</p></div>
</div></section><section id="ref-list1" class="ref-list"><h2 class="pmc_sec_title">References</h2>
